### Adding New Backend Feature
1. Add/update schema in `domain/models/[entity]/` (and related interfaces if needed)
2. Implement business logic in `domain/services/`
3. Register providers/models in `domain.module.ts` (shared domain wiring)
4. Expose use-case via tRPC router in `trpc/routers/[entity].router.ts` (and aggregate in `trpc/router.ts` if needed)
5. If REST exposure is required, add controller/service under `api-v1/`
6. Add/update shared contracts in `libs/shared-types/src/` when shape is cross-package

